            <h1>Light Box</h1>

            <p class="lead">Poet Robert Crawford and photographer Norman McBeath partner to celebrate the 2015 UNESCO International Year of Light.</p>

            <p>The announcement that 2015 was to be the United Nations Educational, Scientific and Cultural Organization (<abbr>UNESCO</abbr>) International Year of Light came at the perfect moment for academic and poet Robert Crawford. Having long been inspired by light and science &mdash; his 1990 poetry debut, <em>A&nbsp;Scottish Assembly</em> weaves together lines on light and love and incorporates tongue-twisting scientific references &mdash; 2015 was also to be the year of an artistic collaboration of poet, photographer and physicist; Light Box. </p>

        </div>

    </div></div></div>

</section>


