            <p>Light Box is a collaborative project between Crawford and Edinburgh photographer Norman McBeath, whose striking portraits play off of the intricacies of light and shadow, with both inspired by contemporary physicists &mdash; including Professor Ifor Samuel at the University of St Andrews &mdash; whose work centres on light. </p>

